    "Android privileged permission allowlists are required only for privileged apps and can break boot if wrong.",
    "Android GSI work requires bootloader, Treble, rollback, and original ROM evidence.",
    "Android DSU is a reversible guest-OS staging path only when supported by the device and trusted images."
