  "notes": [
    "ROM-0 inserts GOFFY as a safe home/system-app payload, not as a privileged OS controller.",
    "App-private memory forget tools are included, approval-gated, and scoped to GOFFY-owned SQLite memory, not phone data or ROM partitions.",
